SUMMARY:🤝 Networking Mixer for Toronto Business Owners & Entrepreneurs
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an intimate evening in downtown Toronto at our March Networking Mixer — designed exclusively for Toronto business owners\, entrepreneurs\, and founders. \nHosted by Toronto Event Hub\, this event offers a unique opportunity to build meaningful connections\, collaborate\, and grow your network as we kick off an exciting year ahead. \nDate: Monday\, March 23\, 2026Time: 7:00 PM – 9:30 PMVenue: Oria on King \n✨ Our events are more intimate that draw 15-40 founders & entrepreneurs from a variety of industries & cities who believe networking should feel genuine — not transactional. \nCheck our events at Toronto Event Hub.
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/%f0%9f%a4%9d-networking-mixer-for-toronto-business-owners-entrepreneurs/
LOCATION:Oria on King\, 220 King St W\, Toronto\, M6G 1B8
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Nightlife
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/f09fa49d-networking-mixer-for-toronto-business-owners-entrepreneurs.png
END:VEVENT
