SUMMARY:Vibraslap! Stand-up Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by comedian and crossword writer Ada Nicolle (Guelph Comedy Festival\, 6.9M+ Instagram views @adanicklmao)\, Vibraslap! is your next favourite alt-comedy show in Toronto. Ada’s chosen some of her favourite stand-up comedians and now you get to see them perform live before they blow up 🙂 \nBring a date! Bring your friends! Bring the mayor! Bring your landlord and you’ll have indie cred with your landlord. Have a meet-cute in the audience! Stop for shawarma on the way home afterward and still get to sleep at a reasonable time. This sounds like the best night ever! (You’re the best at making plans\, y’know; you always are.) \nThis is a queer and trans-friendly comedy show. If Ada is not gay enough for you she will get gayer over the course of the show. \nWanna know the full lineup when it drops? Follow @vibraslapcomedy on Instagram. \nUse SLAP30 for 30% off tickets online.Monday\, March 23rd @ 8:00 PM\, Comedy Bar Bloor\, 945 Bloor St W
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/vibraslap-stand-up-comedy/
LOCATION:Comedy Bar\, 945 Bloor St W\, Toronto\, ON M6H 1L5\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6H 1L5
CATEGORIES:Comedy & Improv
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/vibraslap-stand-up-comedy.png
END:VEVENT
